Title: BMI Buddy: Your Health Companion

Description: BMI Buddy is your go-to tool for understanding your body composition instantly. Input your height and weight to get immediate feedback on your BMI and health category. With a clean interface and customizable integration options, BMI Buddy empowers you to take charge of your wellness journey. Join us in revolutionizing health awareness today!

Features:

Instant BMI feedback
Clear health categorization
User-friendly interface
Customizable integration options
